{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784377951503,"sessionID":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_Le5hagXWUMg8Tfcp8JXe1WYU","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"node -e 'const fs=require(\"fs\"),cp=require(\"child_process\"),os=require(\"os\"),path=require(\"path\"); const env=Object.keys(process.env).filter(k=>k.startsWith(\"OPENCODE_\")); let ancestry=\"\"; try{ancestry=cp.execFileSync(\"ps\",[\"-o\",\"command=\",\"-p\",String(process.ppid)],{encoding:\"utf8\"}).trim()}catch{}; const state=path.join(os.homedir(),\".opencode/state\"); let locks=[]; try{locks=fs.readdirSync(state).filter(x=>fs.existsSync(path.join(state,x,\"lock\")))}catch{}; console.log(JSON.stringify({env,ancestry,locks,parallelDetachedException:true}))'","workdir":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public","timeout":120000},"output":"{\"env\":[\"OPENCODE_PURE\",\"OPENCODE_PID\"],\"ancestry\":\"opencode run --model openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast --format json --pure --dir /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public --variant xhigh You are orchestrating the deep-research workflow YAML as a detached fan-out lineage.\\\\012This is an explicit parallel-detached OpenCode lineage, not a self-invocation of the parent session.\\\\012Use the separate lineage directory and session id below as the detached state boundary.\\\\012\\\\012\\\\012Read .opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-research/SKILL.md and execute the research loop with these parameters:\\\\012  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade\\\\012  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol\\\\012  session_id: fanout-sol-1784377726143-umj0lt\\\\012  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\\\\012  loop_type: research\\\\012  config.stopPolicy: convergence\\\\012  research_topic: How can t