e, not a self-invocation of the parent session.\\\\012Use the separate lineage directory and session id below as the detached state boundary.\\\\012\\\\012\\\\012Read .opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-research/SKILL.md and execute the research loop with these parameters:\\\\012  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade\\\\012  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol\\\\012  session_id: fanout-sol-1784377726143-umj0lt\\\\012  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\\\\012  loop_type: research\\\\012  config.stopPolicy: convergence\\\\012  research_topic: How can the 1,290-style design-token library at .opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/ upgrade the sk-design design-md-generator mode (backend formatters-v3 and the DESIGN.md section schema at .opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/) — as few-shot exemplars, section-schema calibration, token-vocabulary grounding, consistency and quality baselines, and validation fixtures? Build on the retrieval substrate already established in ../001-research-utilization/research/lineages/sol/research.md. Emphasize smart integrations and out-of-the-box ideas that go beyond plain retrieval, and name concrete integration points in the md-generator pipeline with rough build costs.\\\\012  config.maxIterations: 10\\\\012  config.convergenceThreshold: 0.05\\\\012The step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol via the\\\\012config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\\\\012command; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\\\\012\\\\012Run phase_init, phase_main_loop (to legal convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\\\\012Write all outputs to .opencode/sp