{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784378447519,"sessionID":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_xdIoV02EpMTjUh1lB6KeCH18","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"subagent_type":"deep-research","description":"Map md-generator pipeline","command":"/deep:research","prompt":"Execute exactly ONE deep-research LEAF iteration for the detached lineage. Read and follow `.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-001.md` verbatim. This is a workflow-owned single-iteration dispatch, not a request to run or simulate the full loop. Do not dispatch sub-agents. Do not invoke `opencode run`. Write only the three exact iteration outputs permitted by that prompt, verify them, and return a concise completion report."},"output":"<task id=\"ses_08ac57b20ffesoysZF9bUWfTL8\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\n## Iteration 1 Complete\n\n**Focus**: Live md-generator pipeline, schema/prompt assets, and validator boundaries  \n**Findings**: 5 new findings  \n**newInfoRatio**: 1.00  \n**Questions answered**: Q1  \n**Questions remaining**: 4  \n**Edge case**: Contradictory schema/implementation evidence  \n**Next focus**: Corpus-wide section, vocabulary, and absence-pattern calibration\n\n**Files written**:\n- `iterations/iteration-001.md`\n- `deep-research-state.jsonl` — exactly one record appended\n- `deltas/iter-001.jsonl`\n\n**Verification**: All artifacts exist; citations and required sections are complete; canonical state/delta rows match; packet boundary respected; reducer-owned files untouched.\n\n**Status**: complete\n</task_result>\n</task>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","sessionId":"ses_08ac57b20ffesoysZF9bUWfTL8","model":{"modelID":"gpt-5.6-sol-fast","providerID":"openai"},"truncated":false},"title":"Map md-generator pipeline","time":{"start":1784378197222,"end":1784378447514}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_00e82838a057