T or REPORT.\n+- Exemplar rewrites of deterministic target values.\n+- Static prompt template as the only enforceable integration point.\n+\n+## Next Focus\n+\n+Corpus-wide section, Quick Start, token-vocabulary, typography-role, and meaningful-absence calibration for Q2.\n+\n+## Active Risks\n+\n+- Schema-reference, emitter, and validator drift is unresolved.\n+- Spec Kit Memory unavailable; direct canonical evidence is being used.\n+- No convergence or quality-guard stop candidate yet.\n*** Update File: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/orchestration-status.log\n@@\n {\"event\":\"started\",\"label\":\"sol\",\"at\":\"2026-07-18T12:34:32.826Z\",\"duration_ms\":0,\"loop_type\":\"research\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-sol-1784377726143-umj0lt\",\"generation\":1,\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\"},\"gauges\":{\"iterations\":0,\"elapsed_ms\":0,\"score\":0}}\n+{\"event\":\"progress\",\"label\":\"sol\",\"at\":\"2026-07-18T12:38:10.234Z\",\"duration_ms\":217408,\"loop_type\":\"research\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-sol-1784377726143-umj0lt\",\"generation\":1,\"run\":1,\"status\":\"complete\",\"gauges\":{\"iterations\":1,\"elapsed_ms\":217408,\"score\":1.0}}\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-state.jsonl\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-strategy.md\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/findings-registry.json\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-dashboard.md\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/orchestration-