{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784378966282,"sessionID":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_nfbuy14zh11kVrHu0QDWv8LW","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"subagent_type":"deep-research","description":"Calibrate corpus schema","command":"/deep:research","prompt":"Execute exactly ONE deep-research LEAF iteration for the detached lineage. Read and follow `.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-002.md` verbatim. This is a workflow-owned single-iteration dispatch only. Do not dispatch sub-agents or invoke any CLI executor. Write only the three exact outputs permitted by the prompt, verify them, and return a concise completion report."},"output":"<task id=\"ses_08abffcc7ffeamAMcHhAvdew3z\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\n## Iteration 2 Complete\n\n**Focus**: Corpus-calibrated schema, Quick Start coverage, token vocabulary, typography roles, and meaningful absences  \n**Findings**: 5 new  \n**newInfoRatio**: 1.00  \n**Question answered**: Q2  \n**Questions remaining**: 3 (Q3–Q5)  \n**Edge case**: Contradictory radius provenance preserved as a fixture candidate  \n**Next focus**: Q3—bounded study-pair selection and anti-copy controls\n\n**Files written**:\n- `iterations/iteration-002.md`\n- `deep-research-state.jsonl` — exactly one iteration record appended\n- `deltas/iter-002.jsonl`\n\n**Verification**: All artifacts exist; required sections and citations pass; delta first row exactly matches state; packet boundary respected; reducer-owned files untouched.\n\n**Status**: complete\n</task_result>\n</task>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","sessionId":"ses_08abffcc7ffeamAMcHhAvdew3z","model":{"modelID":"gpt-5.6-sol-fast","providerID":"openai"},"truncated":false},"title":"Calibrate corpus schema","time":{"start":1784378557245,"end":1784378966278}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_00b5f023f8dc1d89016a5b74b