{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784379332811,"sessionID":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_qjtIUCsyetAuredIeVJC3TzS","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"subagent_type":"deep-research","description":"Design exemplar protocol","command":"/deep:research","prompt":"Execute exactly ONE deep-research LEAF iteration. Read and follow `.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-003.md` verbatim. This is a workflow-owned single iteration. Do not dispatch sub-agents or invoke any CLI executor. Write only the three allowed outputs, verify them, and return a concise completion report."},"output":"<task id=\"ses_08ab84603ffeLumoVFwFBHpk73\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\n## Iteration 3 Complete\n\n**Focus**: Bounded pre-WRITE STUDY protocol for safe exemplar use  \n**Findings**: 5 new findings  \n**newInfoRatio**: 1.00  \n**Questions answered**: Q3  \n**Questions remaining**: 2  \n**Edge case**: Ambiguous “study pair” interpretation resolved as one bundle’s matched artifacts  \n**Next focus**: Q4—corpus-derived metrics, validators, and fixtures\n\n**Files written**:\n- `iterations/iteration-003.md`\n- `deep-research-state.jsonl` — exactly one record appended\n- `deltas/iter-003.jsonl`\n\n**Verification**: All files exist; citations complete; delta matches the state record; packet boundary respected; reducer-owned files untouched.\n\n**Status**: complete\n</task_result>\n</task>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","sessionId":"ses_08ab84603ffeLumoVFwFBHpk73","model":{"modelID":"gpt-5.6-sol-fast","providerID":"openai"},"truncated":false},"title":"Design exemplar protocol","time":{"start":1784379062785,"end":1784379332803}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_00f1e092cad8c685016a5b76b47e088191802462d4769303f9"}},"id":"prt_f7547b10d001axqz1AfKev2O8a","sessionID":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","messageID":"msg_f75479f