{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784379830202,"sessionID":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_OdYNNic5cDhZmJBw3iTa2JkD","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"subagent_type":"deep-research","description":"Define quality fixtures","command":"/deep:research","prompt":"Execute exactly ONE deep-research LEAF iteration. Read and follow `.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-004.md` verbatim. This is workflow-owned single-iteration work. Do not dispatch sub-agents or invoke CLI executors. Write only the three permitted outputs, verify them, and return a concise completion report."},"output":"<task id=\"ses_08ab28d6cffeWKALNbWx101yW5\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\n## Iteration 4 Complete\n\n**Focus**: Q4 corpus-derived quality baselines, validators, fixtures, CI behavior, and leak thresholds  \n**Findings**: 5 (3 new, 2 partially new)  \n**newInfoRatio**: 0.80  \n**Questions answered**: Q4  \n**Questions remaining**: 1 — Q5  \n**Edge cases**: Two command-quoting failures recovered without evidence loss  \n**Recommended next focus**: Rank integrations by quality lift, dependency order, and build cost\n\n**Files written**:\n- `iterations/iteration-004.md`\n- `deep-research-state.jsonl` — exactly one append\n- `deltas/iter-004.jsonl`\n\n**Verification**:\n- Outputs exist: yes\n- Findings cited: yes\n- Delta first row matches state: yes\n- Packet boundary respected: yes\n- Reducer-owned files untouched: yes\n\n**Status**: complete\n</task_result>\n</task>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","sessionId":"ses_08ab28d6cffeWKALNbWx101yW5","model":{"modelID":"gpt-5.6-sol-fast","providerID":"openai"},"truncated":false},"title":"Define quality fixtures","time":{"start":1784379437721,"end":1784379830198}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0a687efbb739474e016a5b782b62e881919d34b29068624df9"}},"id":"prt_f754d6980001OliD8rboqcdzhQ","sessionID":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","messageID":"msg_f754d5859001tCMTYg6fL6Aihm"}}
