ion.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-005.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-005.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-005.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-005.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,41 @@\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteration 5 Prompt Pack\n+\n+## State\n+\n+STATE SUMMARY:\n+Segment: 1 | Iteration: 5 of 10\n+Questions: 4/5 answered | Last focus: quality baselines, validators, and fixtures\n+Last 2 ratios: 1.00 -> 0.80 | Stuck count: 0\n+Minimum iteration floor: passed.\n+Memory context: unavailable; direct evidence is authoritative.\n+Next focus: Answer Q5 with a decision-grade ranking of all upgrade levers by quality lift, dependency order, implementation risk, and build cost. Define phased MVP, later optional layers, explicit defer/reject list, concrete file-level integration points, and at least three out-of-the-box ideas whose value goes beyond plain retrieval.\n+\n+Research Topic: How the 1,290-style corpus should materially upgrade design-md-generator as exemplars, schema/vocabulary calibration, quality baselines, fixtures, and smart integrations.\n+\n+Remaining Key Question: Q5.\n+Last 3 