rections.\n+- Check whether Q1-Q5 can legally converge after this iteration and identify any remaining non-blocking calibration unknowns.\n+- Do not implement. Only write the exact narrative, one canonical state append, and exact delta. Include route proof and all required fields; delta first row must match state.\n+- Narrative sections: Focus, Actions Taken, Findings, Ruled Out, Dead Ends, Edge Cases, Sources Consulted, Assessment, Reflection, Recommended Next Focus.\n+- Return a concise completion report only after verification.\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-005.md","relativePath":".opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-005.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-005.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-005.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-005.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,41 @@\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteration 5 Prompt Pack\n+\n+## State\n+\n+STATE SUMMARY:\n+Segment: 1 | Iteration: 5 of 10\n+Questions: 4/5 answered | Last focus: quality baselines, validators, and fixtures\n+Last 2 ratios: 1.00 -> 0.80 | Stuck count: 0\n+Minimum iteration floor: passed.\n+Memory context: unavailable; direct evidence is authoritative.\n+Next focus: Answer Q5 with a decision-grade ranking of all upgrade levers by quality lift, dependency order, implementation risk, and build cost. Define phased MVP, later optional layers, explicit defer/reject list, concrete file-level integration points, and at least three out-of-the-box ideas whose value goes beyond plain retrieval.\n+\n+Research Topic: How the 1,290-style corpus should materially upgrade design-md-generator as exemplars, schema/vocabulary calibration, quality baselines, fixtures, and smart integrations.\n+\n+Remaining Key Question: Q5.\n+Last 3 Iterations Summary: run 2 schema calibration (1.00); run 3 STUDY protocol (1.00); run 4 validation/fixtures (0.80).\n+\n+## State Files\n+\n+- Config: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-config.json\n+- State Log: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-state.jsonl\n+- Strategy: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-strategy.md\n+- Registry: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/findings-registry.json\n+- Write narrative: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-005.md\n+- Write delta: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deltas/iter-005.jsonl\n+\n+## Constraints\n+\n+- Execute exactly one LEAF iteration; no sub-agents or CLI dispatch.\n+- Read state and the prior four iteration findings first. Use narrow source verification only where load-bearing ranking or file-level attachment claims need confirmation.\n+- Produce a ranked lever table or equivalent decision structure with quality lift, prerequisites, risk, rough incremental cost, and named file/symbol/stage attachment points.\n+- Avoid double-counting overlapping estimates. Distinguish total phased effort from standalone lever costs and state assumptions about the predecessor retrieval substrate.\n+- Include at least three smart, out-of-the-box ideas that are evidence-compatible and go beyond retrieval, such as counterfactual capability probes, schema drift sentinels, diversity-preserving calibration, or target-fact mutation testing. Rank them honestly.\n+- Define MVP, hardening, and optional/deferred phases; explicitly reject high-cost/low-evidence directions.\n+- Check whether Q1-Q5 can legally converge after this iteration and identify any remaining non-blocking calibration unknowns.\n+- Do not implement. Only write the exact narrative, one canonical state append, and exact delta. Include route proof and all required fields; delta first row must match state.\n+- Narrative sections: Focus, Actions Taken, Findings, Ruled Out, Dead Ends, Edge Cases, Sources Consulted, Assessment, Reflection, Recommended Next Focus.\n+- Return a concise completion report only after verification.\n","additions":41,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-005.md","time":{"start":1784380018659,"end":1784380018664}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_07c9c38e03d705e1016a5b7a6258d4819196768a3f5bd49c82"}},"id":"prt_f755610380010bSuGrTtMkHW3Y","sessionID":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","messageID":"msg_f75560187001LZQpPAuAFtArHg"}}
