{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784380371356,"sessionID":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_eZ89GlaaF0csNBxQuMmjWUjr","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"subagent_type":"deep-research","description":"Rank upgrade levers","command":"/deep:research","prompt":"Execute exactly ONE deep-research LEAF iteration. Read and follow `.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-005.md` verbatim. This is workflow-owned single-iteration work. Do not dispatch sub-agents or invoke CLI executors. Write only the three permitted outputs, verify them, and return a concise completion report."},"output":"<task id=\"ses_08aa98fdbffekM11WoQGagSwYr\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\n## Iteration 5 Complete\n\n**Focus**: Ranked upgrade levers, phased costs, integration points, and convergence eligibility  \n**Findings**: 5 findings (2 new, 3 partially new)  \n**newInfoRatio**: 0.80  \n**Questions answered**: Q5  \n**Questions remaining**: 0  \n**Edge cases**: None; numeric convergence remains unmet because 0.80 exceeds 0.05  \n**Recommended next focus**: Narrow convergence/calibration verification only\n\n**Files written**:\n- `iterations/iteration-005.md`\n- `deep-research-state.jsonl` — exactly one record appended\n- `deltas/iter-005.jsonl`\n\n**Verification**:\n- Iteration file exists: yes\n- JSONL iteration append count: 1\n- Delta first row exactly matches state record: yes\n- Findings citations complete: yes\n- Packet boundary respected: yes\n- Reducer-owned files untouched: yes\n\n**Status**: complete\n</task_result>\n</task>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_08acca7b4ffeXv97nbzMOKS10V","sessionId":"ses_08aa98fdbffekM11WoQGagSwYr","model":{"modelID":"gpt-5.6-sol-fast","providerID":"openai"},"truncated":false},"title":"Rank upgrade levers","time":{"start":1784380026917,"end":1784380371351}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_097f3998a8e74554016a5b7a