al controls are schema-drift sentinels, counterfactual capability probes, and diversity-preserving calibration.\n@@\n - Corpus medians as hard gates, raw corpus test snapshots, and automatic fixture blessing in CI.\n+- Vector replatforming, model fine-tuning, and LLM-as-judge enforcement without a measured residual gap.\n@@\n-Decision-grade lever ranking, phased MVP, costs, risks, and out-of-the-box integrations for Q5.\n+Synthesis complete; proceed to implementation planning from the ranked Phase A/Phase B sequence.\n@@\n-- No convergence or quality-guard stop candidate yet.\n+- Remaining unknowns are implementation calibration only: exact warning weights, leak precision, retrieval packaging, and measured task duration.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-config.json\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-strategy.md\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/findings-registry.json\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-dashboard.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-config.json\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-config.json\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/002-md-generator-upgrade/research/line